skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cylinder says
des:
4 year old tested wiggle game! This is similar to Simon Says but with the phrase, "Cylinder Says".

Start this skill by saying "Alexa, open cylinder says" or "Alexa, ask cylinder says to play" and then get ready to get some wiggles out while playing cylinder says. At the end of the round, say "start" or "begin" to play again. This is sure to keep your child/children wiggling and laughing for a while!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
